      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly like a new car. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, showroom state with no signs of wear. Under the hood, the engine and transmission perform perfectly, reflecting meticulous maintenance and very careful ownership. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in its original, factory-perfect state.",
